l":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8yl","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":2845,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/10\/allah-forgives-mistakes-coercion\/","url_meta":{"origin":32881,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Pardon: Allah forgives honest mistakes, coerced sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has pardoned my nation for their mistakes, their forgetfulness, and what they are coerced into doing.\u201d Source: Sunan\u00a0Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2043 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0630\u064e\u0631\u064d\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/07\/27\/forgot-salawat-ala-nabi\/","url_meta":{"origin":32881,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Forgetting to send blessings on the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets to send blessings upon me, he has missed the path to Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 908 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3469,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/03\/hudud-fard-limits\/","url_meta":{"origin":32881,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Law: Allah has made duties, limits, do not transgress","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tha\u2019laba reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has made duties obligatory, do not neglect them. He has set limits, do not transgress them. He has made some things sacred, do no violate them. He has remained silent upon matters as mercy\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26480,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/31\/accidental-no-make-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":32881,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: No make up fasts if broken accidentally","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever breaks his fast forgetfully in the month of Ramadan, there is no compensation or expiation for it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3521 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36323,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/25\/hour-approaching\/","url_meta":{"origin":32881,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hour: Hereafter approaching, people forgetful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour is approaching people, yet it does not increase but in distance from their minds.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 10\/13 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15381,"url":"https:\/\/www.abu